script(type="text/x-template")#login-form
.login.js-login.js__rotate-card#login-component
	.login__title
		h2.subtitle.login__title-txt Авторизуйтесь
	
	form.form-login#js-form-login
		.js-error-login.js-error-login_login Введите логин
		.js-error-login.js-error-login_password Введите пароль
		.js-error-login.js-error-login_checkbox Вы не человек
		.js-error-login.js-error-login_radio Вы не уверены, что Вы человек
		.js-sucsess-login 
			.js-sucsess-text Введите верные логин и пароль!
			button.js-suscess-btn(type="button") Закрыть
		.form-login__input-row
			.form-login__input-before.form-login__input-before_login
			input(type='text' class='form-login__input js-form-login_login' name='form-login__login' placeholder='Логин' v-model="user.name")
		.form-login__input-row
			.form-login__input-before.form-login__input-before_password
			input(type='password' class='form-login__input js-form-login_password' name='form-login__password' placeholder='Пароль' v-model="user.password")
		.form-login__checkbox-block
			label.form-login__checkbox-label
				input(type='checkbox' id='checkbox__login' checked tabindex='0' ).form-login__checkbox.js-form-login_checkbox 
				.form-login__checkbox-custom
				label.form-login__checkbox-text(for='checkbox__login') Я человек
			
		.form-login-robot Вы точно не робот?
		.form-login-radio-row
			label.form-login-radio-label
				input.form-login-radio.js-form-login_radio(type='radio' id='form-login-radio-yes' name='form-login-radio' value='yes' checked)
				.form-login-radio-block
					.form-login-radio-custom(tabindex='0')
					label.form-login-radio-text(for='form-login-radio-yes') Да
				
			label.form-login-radio-label
				input(type='radio' id='form-login-radio-no' name='form-login-radio' value='no').form-login-radio.js-form-login_radio
				.form-login-radio-block
					.form-login-radio-custom(tabindex='0')
					label.form-login-radio-text(for='form-login-radio-no') Не уверен
				
				
		.form-login-buttons-row
			button.form-login-button.form-login-button-main.js-tomain-btn(type='button') На главную
			button.form-login-button.form-login-button-login(type='submit' v-on:submit="123") Войти